It immediately makes my mouth pucker and makes it feel like my mouth is being
dissolved and corroded. It's stupid sour. On the aftertaste it tastes like
artificial cherries, up front it's just pure sour. By far it's the most sour
Ghost I've had, and trust me, they're all pretty sour. Not for the faint of
heart, and arguably the least refreshing one. It confuses me how they seem to
want to maintain themselves as a preworkout energy drink yet all their flavors
are super sour so not very refreshing.

